Chemistry::File::SMARTS version 0.21
====================================

This object-oriented module is used for reading SMARTS patterns, returning
Chemistry::Pattern objects.

For more information about SMARTS, see the SMARTS Theory Manual at
http://www.daylight.com/dayhtml/doc/theory/theory.smarts.html

CHANGES SINCE VERSION 0.20
    - Fixed parsing bug where Br was interpreted as "boron in a ring", among
      other two-letter symbols.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:
        Chemistry::Mol          0.24
        Chemistry::Pattern      0.25
        Chemistry::Ring         0.16
        Chemistry::File::SMILES 0.41
        List::Util              0
        Test::More              0

